<p>You host a small server that is solar powered</p>
<h2 id="problem">Problem</h2>
<p>Sometimes the battery runs out on a cloudy day. Users need a way to see how much time they have left to browse before the site goes offline</p>
<h2 id="solution">Solution</h2>
<p>Have a powerbar that surfaces the battery % to all users</p>
